{"tid":1549723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成立獨立調查委員會已經太遲，一定要解散警隊。","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:40.000Z","uid":105538,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2fdf5dd357a1f9348ee5665f3a5f9bd037ddad","tid":1549723,"uid":105538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"監警會一直都冇用大家都知<br />\n<br />\n所以先要成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n如果兩個月前成立 相信大家都會收貨<br />\n<br />\n但去到今日 it is too late. Just too late.<br />\n<br />\n經歷左三個月每日警察既濫權濫捕暴力襲擊市民<br />\n<br />\n有警棍扑頭 圍毆 屈斷手腕 橡膠子彈射盲眼 希袋彈 催淚彈向頭射等等已經數之不盡既暴行<br />\n<br />\n但係警員身上冇號碼識別 冇配帶委任證<br />\n幪面 用強光燈射記者鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n根本有再公正既法官審判都唔會緝拿到真正既元凶<br />\n<br />\n所以去到依刻訴求一定要升級<br />\n<br />\n一定要解散警隊 提升警隊入職學歷條件<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最新訴求：解散警隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 及更改口號<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"9143063dda431bf6db7cd8dc020d09f9ee6e3bbd","tid":1549723,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e9b01fcdc76065c6ce6cd8289a0a47e14dc1d28","tid":1549723,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de9aaed1f970b3fb9936af83f57ac0a1016acf8","tid":1549723,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fc7c8887fabe23f8119d301f7d5b03ce93e06d16","tid":1549723,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7b97fe810bb2af196c5d9506532f4a9cd21922f","tid":1549723,"uid":69158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"解散警隊比公安進場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a540db847e5d6f134bba45160c65ec9cccbf421","tid":1549723,"uid":269216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"Even比你提高到入職門檻，有學歷點解有人唔做要去做狗先@@?"},{"pid":"58780ca6c7a8a2a3bb65899adc7fc6aafd810c40","tid":1549723,"uid":105042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"就算你唔支持解散警隊，最低限度一定要 剷除警察投訴課，佢地先係問題根源，直接令到監警會完全失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1dfeb3dcf12216e087e7d9db94da9c1e6687a5","tid":1549723,"uid":319458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"解散警隊冇咩可能<br />\n但就一定要清算有份濫權濫捕暴力既黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0f57f97198e6895913b98c3895b53bd880e793","tid":1549723,"uid":1372